'''波霸餐廳'''（{{lang-en|'''Breastaurant'''}}）<ref>{{cite news |title=美「波霸餐廳」主打火辣服務生　辣翻雙眼再填飽肚子 |url=http://health.nownews.com/2012/07/13/11847-2827793.htm |publisher=nownews |date=2012-06-25 |accessdate=2014-03-29 }}{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>是指一種以[[乳房|胸部]]豐滿（[[波霸|波霸]]）性感女[[服務生|服務生]]為特色的[[餐馆|餐廳]]，女服務生會穿著低胸清涼的[[制服|制服]]（例如[[細肩帶|細肩帶]][[背心|背心]]和[[熱褲|熱褲]]）。此一詞語的出現大約是在1990年代初期，也就是[[Hooters|Hooters]]餐廳在美國開始流行的時候<ref name="esquire">{{cite web | url=http://www.esquire.com/blogs/food-for-men/breastaurant-chains-5999331 | title=Hostess of the Week, 'Breastaurant' Edition | accessdate=2012-06-28 | author=Mikin, Mark | date=2011-06-27 | archive-date=2014-12-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141209101704/http://www.esquire.com/blogs/food-for-men/breastaurant-chains-5999331 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。很多類似的餐廳也有相近的服務，像{{link-en|Tilted Kilt Pub & Eatery餐廳|Tilted Kilt Pub & Eatery}}<ref name="boingboing">{{cite web | url=http://www.boingboing.net/2011/06/08/breastaurants-are-ho.html | title="Breastaurants" are Hooters 2.0 | accessdate=2012-06-28 | author=Doctorow, Cory | date=2011-06-08 | archive-date=2020-12-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207104253/https://boingboing.net/2011/06/08/breastaurants-are-ho.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[双峰_(连锁餐厅)|雙峰餐廳]]、Bombshells、Ojos Locos、{{link-en|Bikinis Sports Bar & Grill餐廳||Bikinis Sports Bar & Grill}}、Show-Me's、Brick House Tavern、Mugs & Jugs、及{{link-en|Heart Attack Grill餐廳|Heart Attack Grill}}等。

這類餐廳不論在裝潢或是菜單上都有有特定的主題，一般會提供顧客包括酒精飲料<!--and [[Flirting|flirty]] servers.-->在內的許多福利<ref name="boingboing" />。依照[[Yahoo|Yahoo]]的定義，波霸餐廳的賣點有以下四項：服務、食物、娛樂及乳房<ref>{{cite web | url=http://news.yahoo.com/breastaurant-boom-why-hooters-knockoffs-thriving-110500797.html | title=The 'breastaurant' boom: Why Hooters knockoffs are thriving | accessdate=2012-06-28 | author=The Week's Editorial Staff | date=2012-06-26 | archive-date=2019-06-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190618001420/https://news.yahoo.com/breastaurant-boom-why-hooters-knockoffs-thriving-110500797.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.foxnews.com/us/2012/06/24/breastaurant-boom-hooters-style-eateries-experience-mini-boom/ |title=Breastaurants experiencing a mini-boom |access-date=2014-03-28 |archive-date=2015-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009051615/http://www.foxnews.com/us/2012/06/24/breastaurant-boom-hooters-style-eateries-experience-mini-boom/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

一般認為[[Hooters|Hooters]]是第一家波霸餐廳，自1980年代起開始營運，其他的餐廳也很快開始仿效<ref name="indianexpress">{{cite web | url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/breastaurants-with-view-booming-in-struggling-us-dining-industry/967358/ | title='Breastaurants' with 'view' booming in struggling US dining industry | accessdate=2012-06-28 | author=Agencies | date=2012-06-27 | archive-date=2013-10-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021010030/http://www.indianexpress.com/news/breastaurants-with-view-booming-in-struggling-us-dining-industry/967358 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。依照食品產業研究公司Technomic的分析資料，在2011年美國除了Hooters以外的最三大波霸餐廳，營業額成長了30%，雖然只有美國頂級餐廳營業額的1%，不過也比像{{link-en|Applebee's餐廳|Applebee's}}和{{link-en|Bennigan's||Bennigan's}}的表現要好，後面二個餐廳在2008年的[[經濟大衰退|經濟大衰退]]時，有出現營業額的下降<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2164066/Growth-breastaurant-Waitresses-offering-dinner-view-support-dining-industrys-sole-uptick-sales.html | title=The breast restaurant guide: How waitresses offering dinner and a tacky 'view' are keeping U.S. diners alive in the recession | accessdate=2012-06-28 | author=Daily Mail Reporter | date=2012-06-24 | archive-date=2020-08-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813154423/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2164066/Growth-breastaurant-Waitresses-offering-dinner-view-support-dining-industrys-sole-uptick-sales.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

美國的{{link-en|Bikinis Sports Bar & Grill餐廳||Bikinis Sports Bar & Grill}}在2012年10月成功的向[[美国专利及商标局|美国专利及商标局]]註冊將Breastaurant為其註冊商標<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.trademarkia.com/breastaurant-85416160.html | title=USPTO Trademark: Breastaurant | accessdate=2012-06-28 | author=Trademarkia | date=2013-04-24 | archive-date=2018-03-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180314174619/https://www.trademarkia.com/breastaurant-85416160.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

